{"word":"H8427 - תָּוָה - tâvâh - taw-vaw' - Scrabble","slug":"H8427","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">תָּוָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tâvâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>taw-vaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Scrabble"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05D4; - ta&#x0302;va&#x0302;h</b> - <i>taw-vaw'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>mark</i> out, that is, (primitive) <i>scratch</i> or (definitely) <i>imprint: - </i>scrabble, set [a mark]."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8379\">H8379</a>, <a href=\"#/H8420\">H8420</a>"}]}